location.fullValue: Julian Plan, The Springs at Skyline Trails

data.description: Beautiful home in Settlers Ridge addition in Yukon. 3 bed 2.5 bath with study and closet that could be used as a 4th bedroom. 2,090 sqft. New flooring and paint. Home has many updated fixtures. Very nice open concept between kitchen, living and dining room. Storm shelter. New outdoor building with dog run. Very convenient location for dining and close access to I-40. Buyer is to verify schools.
